{
  "stem": "323.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, he worked in the-- in an-- with the organization, he was in the office.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had a secretary who also lived with us, who was also Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think things-- that's when things first started to change and that I was aware of, that it wasn't so nifty to be a Jew in Germany.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish holidays?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We always--we belonged to a temple in Bielefeld.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, I went to Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the most a hundred, at the very most, not that many.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Bielefeld at that time probably had about half a million people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "M-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In West-- Westphalia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not too far from Hanover.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most people know Hanover better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, things really began to change with Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the first time that I really became aware of what will be.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my parents didn't really talk to us about it, because-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't want-- I guess they didn't want to upset us or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I was told about it after Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before that, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there were-- I mean, we were the only Jewish family on the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no prejudice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I played with all my friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was just when-- when I started wearing the Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's when people became aware of it and all that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was about 30-- in '38, after, '39.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "M-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember my mother crying hysterically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was never taken to a concentration camp, because he worked for this organization.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember my aunt coming over because my uncle had been taken to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is this cousin I told you about that was in school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'38.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right after they smashed everything in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know about it until the next day.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
